title: KENNEL CARETAKER P/T, weekends, & on call position. Must
text:
KENNEL CARETAKER P/T, weekends, & on call position. Must ad date: 10/02/2015 
KENNEL CARETAKER P/T, weekends, & on call position. Must be able to work with dogs up to 130 lbs, clean/ maintain kennel areas (including janitorial & light maintenance) and general computer skills knowledge. Applicant must have a valid CA DL, vehicle, current tetanus shot and able to lift 50 lbs. Back ground check required. No phone calls. Mail app. to: P.O. Box 830 Jamestown, CA 95327.
